data.description: Opportunity is ready with this home.  Home is sitting on two parcels and is a corner lot. Main floor is host to the 3 bedrooms, kitchen, separate dining room (use as office if needed) and then living room. Full basement that is partially finished with a great family room space for entertaining or enjoying time with the family.  Out the back door you will walk out onto full concrete area that leads to the double car garage, or sit back and enjoy a swim in just the right size inground pool or BBQ with family and/or friends under the covered area of deck by the pool. Located just 33 miles from St. Louis International Airport, this home has the easy commutes available and centrally located to several communities with ample shopping, restaurants and businesses. Culp Lane Community Park is a very coinvent 1.8 miles away.  Use your skills and imagine this home ready for your family or investment opportunity.  Home is SOLD AS IS. Seller will not satisfy occupancy or make repairs.
